<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><hymn_number>339</hymn_number>
<title>JESUH KA DAWT TAKTAK CH339</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 Ka theih duhmi minsung a um, A sunnak sak ka duh, Tingtang thawng bang
 ka hnathlam ah, Leicung a thlum bik min.

[C1]
   Jesuh ka dawt taktak, Jesuh ka dawt taktak Jesuh ka dawt taktak, A
   ka dawt hmasa ca'h.

[V2]
 Keimah tlanh awk thimi khamhtu, Dawtnak kong a ka chimh, Misual
 thlacamnak a thi sung, Chuakmi kong a ka chimh.

[C2]
   Jesuh ka dawt taktak, Jesuh ka dawt taktak Jesuh ka dawt taktak, A
   ka dawt hmasa ca'h.

[V3]
 Ka Pa nih ni fatin kei ca, A khonmi kong a chim, A muimi lam ka kal
 zongah, Ka lam ni a tlanter.

[C3]
   Jesuh ka dawt taktak, Jesuh ka dawt taktak Jesuh ka dawt taktak, A
   ka dawt hmasa ca'h.

[V4]
 Ka ngaih-chiatnak a thei khotu, Jesuh kong a ka chimh, Mi phorh khawh
 lo ka ngaih-chiatnak, Phorh awkah a ka bawmh.

[C4]
   Jesuh ka dawt taktak, Jesuh ka dawt taktak Jesuh ka dawt taktak, A
   ka dawt hmasa ca'h.</lyrics>
<key>Ab</key>
</song>